<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h3 class="h2-heading-ss">
      The importance of 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        provenance and documentation
      </span>
    </h3>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      Provenance and documentation are important factors to consider when authenticating a Balenciaga handbag. Here are some things to look for:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Dust bag and box:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         The bag should come with a dust bag and a box, which are standard inclusions for authentic Balenciaga items.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Clear and legible label:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should have a clear and legible label with the Balenciaga logo, ensuring that the branding is consistent with the brand’s standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Consistent stitching pattern:</h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should have a consistent and even stitching pattern, reflecting the high-quality craftsmanship of Balenciaga.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third article_column-text-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <h4 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100 tal">Serial number or certificate of authenticity: </h4>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The bag should have a serial number or a certificate of authenticity, providing proof of its genuineness.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="body-text tac block-bottom-text w-100">
      By ensuring that your Balenciaga bag comes with proper provenance and documentation, you can confidently verify its authenticity and enjoy your luxury purchase.
  </p>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Three text columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns article_three-text-columns rebranding-wider-section-bottom",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}